      <title>乌克兰否认援助袭击马里瓦格纳部队的叛军</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/ukraine-denies-aiding-rebels-who-attacked-malian-wagner-forces</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰最高外交官否认乌克兰向马里分离主义叛军提供支持，这些叛军在上个月的冲突中杀害了数十名政府军和瓦格纳集团雇佣兵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/ukraine-denies-aiding-rebels-who-attacked-malian-wagner-forces</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 12:23:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索马里内阁批准 2026 年选举实行一人一票制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/somalia-s-cabinet-approves-one-person-one-vote-system-for-2026</link>
      <description><![CDATA[索马里内阁部长批准了一项选举法，该法将于 2026 年实施一人一票制度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/somalia-s-cabinet-approves-one-person-one-vote-system-for-2026</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 11:15:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡将“加倍努力”保持生活成本稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/singapore-to-redouble-efforts-to-keep-costs-of-living-stable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡总理黄循财承诺将“加倍努力”应对高昂的生活成本，包括加强对最弱势群体的社会安全网。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/singapore-to-redouble-efforts-to-keep-costs-of-living-stable</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 10:59:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
