      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/singapore-sees-challenges-amid-vicious-turn-in-world-politics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于许多国家的政治出现“恶性转变”，新加坡领导人警告未来将面临挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/singapore-sees-challenges-amid-vicious-turn-in-world-politics</guid>
