    <item>
      <title>嫌疑人策划维也纳泰勒·斯威夫特演唱会爆炸、刺伤事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/suspect-planned-bombing-stabbings-at-vienna-taylor-swift-show</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据奥地利情报部门负责人称，奥地利警方周三逮捕了一名袭击嫌疑人，该嫌疑人计划使用自制炸药和刀具袭击泰勒·斯威夫特维也纳演唱会的观众。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/suspect-planned-bombing-stabbings-at-vienna-taylor-swift-show</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 10:45:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯因乌克兰军队袭击宣布边境地区进入紧急状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/russia-calls-kursk-emergency-after-kyiv-sends-troops-over-border</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰军队对俄罗斯领土发动了自两年多前克里姆林宫发动战争以来最大规模的入侵，俄罗斯宣布西部地区进入紧急状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/russia-calls-kursk-emergency-after-kyiv-sends-troops-over-border</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 10:10:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加泰罗尼亚分离主义者普伊格蒙特违抗法庭判决，返回西班牙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/catalan-separatist-puigdemont-defies-courts-with-return-to-spain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前加泰罗尼亚主席卡莱斯·普伊格蒙特 (Carles Puigdemont) 出现在巴塞罗那的一场集会上，尽管因挪用公款而遭到逮捕，他还是结束了近七年的自我流放，返回了西班牙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/catalan-separatist-puigdemont-defies-courts-with-return-to-spain</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 07:26:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚鲁托在抗议活动再度升温的阴影下宣誓就任内阁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/kenya-s-ruto-swears-in-cabinet-in-shadow-of-renewed-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管肯尼亚民众重启反政府抗议活动并导致数十人丧生，但总统威廉·鲁托仍任命了 19 名经议会批准的部长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/kenya-s-ruto-swears-in-cabinet-in-shadow-of-renewed-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:24:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非加大力度退出黑钱名单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/south-africa-needs-more-political-will-to-exit-dirty-money-list</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非金融监管机构一位高级官员表示，南非正在加大力度解决打击非法资金流动方面的不足，以便摆脱全球黑钱名单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/south-africa-needs-more-political-will-to-exit-dirty-money-list</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国抗议活动缓和后，斯塔默誓言将继续对暴徒施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/anti-racism-protesters-give-uk-some-respite-after-days-of-riots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默坚称，尽管预计当晚会发生骚乱，但因警方和数千名反种族主义抗议者的大力支持而得以避免，当局仍将继续打击困扰英国街头的极右翼暴力骚乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/anti-racism-protesters-give-uk-some-respite-after-days-of-riots</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 23:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
